Curl cheet sheet: http://daniel.haxx.se/blog/2015/09/16/a-curl-cheat-sheet/
https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=10235974

See also https://github.com/jkbrzt/httpie
for a curl like with a nicer cli
For tests: http://httpbin.org/

-L: follow redirects
-k: insecure (don't check certificates)
-s: silent (-sS: still show errors)
-v: verbose

curl -O ploum
curl -o file ploum

http example.org/file > file
http --download example.org/file
--follow
